        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>United States Ports of Entry Threat and Operational Review Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs U.S. Customs and Border Protection to submit to the congressional homeland security and tax committees a threat and operational analysis of U.S. air, land, and sea ports of entry.</p>]]></text>
